PROFESSOR: No.

00:18:13.410 --> 00:18:14.230
Lambda emission.

00:18:14.230 --> 00:18:18.330
Is it going to be greater than
or less than lambda incident?

00:18:18.330 --> 00:18:19.130
Ready?

00:18:19.130 --> 00:18:20.602
Three, two, one.

00:18:20.602 --> 00:18:21.560
AUDIENCE: Greater than.

00:18:21.560 --> 00:18:22.730
PROFESSOR: Greater than.

00:18:22.730 --> 00:18:27.030
So this thing is
